import React from 'react'
import { Container,Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
export const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <footer>
            <Container>
            <Row>
                < Col className="text-right py-3">
                    Copyright © FUND-TRACKER
                </Col>
                
   
          </Row>
          <Row Row className="text-centre py-3">
                    CONTACT US AT
         </Row>
         <Row Row className="text-centre py-3">
                    +000111999
         </Row>

         <Row Row className="text-centre py-3">
                help@donate-
         </Row>
          </Container> 
        </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
